油 堅持 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我知冇可能日日都去，但連續兩日去係必需，如果唔係就正中SHK高層下懷，我地根本就只係去一日打卡趁墟！聽日後日之後都可以唔再去，但今日，今日一定要再去，等佢地唔知究竟件事會維持幾耐，要佢地怕，佢地先會回應！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日，八點，不見不散！<br />\n希望大家，團結，堅持，<br />\n新地高層咪龜縮<br />\n否則商鋪冇人租！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a692839e2f545cddea53cda05ad9d9b6e7c47b80","tid":1325950,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:03:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3ffed91afb199701db934d275e1636f74c1edee","tid":1325950,"uid":280305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e1496b4f34faaf817237df262cd0b14ed7eded8","tid":1325950,"uid":208180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D7ymH31tvWU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD7ymH31tvWU&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=81bb112e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D7ymH31tvWU</a><br />\n<br />\n我地啲投訴你唔正視？<br />\n咁我寫夠100張俾你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"20:00先至去冇用！要日頭去！下午至傍晚！"},{"pid":"6cbc83b65e71ae5a13d094dee07cdf1274c66678","tid":1325950,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"Office time去佢辦公室啦<br />\n<br />\n野餐裝備重點po 幫推pls<br />\n【遊戲更新：終極裝備攻略】我在香城Online 2.0 等你～～<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322657</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣遊行不如由金鐘行返落銅鑼灣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323421</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂][精簡篇]裝備及防火須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[721 廣傳] 兄弟爬山 對抗暴徒 物資採購攻略 - Decathlon<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324768\" data-auto-link target=